headline: 2 Tech Dividend Stocks to Buy and Hold for a Decade
summary: Investors should be aware though that plenty of excellent dividend companies exist in other sectors, including the technology sector, which is often the favorite destination of growth-oriented investors.  Meta Platforms, the parent company of Facebook, initiated its dividend payout last year.
